c: 29
v: 46
t: "Futhi ningaphikisani nabantu bencwadi ngaphandle kwaleyo (ndlela) engcono kakhulu, ngaphandle kwalabo abenza okungalungile phakathi kwabo futhi yithini, “siyakholwa kulokho okwambulwa kuthina nokwambulwa kunina futhi uNkulunkulu wethu noNkulunkulu wenu munye futhi thina siyazithoba ngaphansi kwentando yakhe"